{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":554188,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同意","timestamp":1605350667,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554189,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"学校没有引导是真的，这部分学生放不下过去的成绩过于悲观也是真的，既然改变不了客观环境，先从改变自己开始吧","timestamp":1605350685,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554197,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"学校从来没考虑过这些学生的需求","timestamp":1605350794,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554199,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同意 感觉学校到辅导员到学长学姐对成绩差的同学的建议基本都是：“好好努力把成绩提上去”“成绩很重要” 但只要有排名就一定会有最后的人，唉","timestamp":1605350830,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554228,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"这些人并没有被世一大当作自己的学生吧","timestamp":1605351249,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554240,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 是啊……","timestamp":1605351440,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554262,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"诶，所有人只会告诉你往前走，前面有什么，说一些不痛不痒的挑不出毛病的话，没人去关心后面的同学怎么办","timestamp":1605351756,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554267,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同意","timestamp":1605351767,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554268,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Hans","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Eve: 同意","timestamp":1605351780,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554275,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Isabella","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"是的诶sigh","timestamp":1605351857,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554322,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我觉得这还真不能怪老师导员，毕竟他们能留校就已经是竞争中的胜利者了，他们中的大部分根本理解不了后进群体的难过，没有体验过失败滋味的人再怎么说话也都是不痛不痒的","timestamp":1605352492,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554343,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Jason","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"尤其清华这种标准，选老师的根据是学术水平，根本没有对共情能力的考察。很多老师本身自己就是理工科一根筋（尤其是比较年轻的老师），怎么辅导别人？","timestamp":1605352769,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554355,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Kate","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"同意","timestamp":1605352946,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554374,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Louis","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Jason: 整体同意，不排除个别人有","timestamp":1605353285,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":554603,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Margaret","permissions":["report"],"pid":115531,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"会有人听劝嘛，说得好像有人信","timestamp":1605357179,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":26,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":115531,"reply":15,"tag":null,"text":"我感觉学校应该加强对成绩差的学生的引导和教育，尤其是让他们知道成绩差的学生也能有不错的前途，外推、工作什么的也不错，起码不至于让这部分学生因为卷不动而绝望，甚至自杀。很可惜，清华的“成绩差就是垃圾废物，没前途的”价值观已经深入骨髓了。","timestamp":1605350577,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782641,"url":"","vote":{}}}